title: Strangers in Paradise, Volume 5: Immortal Enemies
description: Strangers In Paradise: Immortal Enemies is the ongoing tale of three friends, Katchoo, Francine and David. This volume finds Katchoo leaving her beloved Francine to look for David, the only male friend she's ever had, but finds his wicked sister Darcy Parker instead. Given an offer she can't refuse, Katchoo is forced to return to work for Darcy in the sordid world of sex and politics, or lose Francine forever. When Francine enlists the aid of Det. Walsh to help find Katchoo, she soon discovers the horrible secrets her friend has been hiding-secrets that may destroy them both!
author: Terry Moore
